{"id":"f6cdedc37518ddf03b8653868b56020b10dc684c395f8f062278c2001050375b","item_id":"c1812aa016:0","text":"此 pattern 提供与"}
{"id":"cdeca50a697f0260135dc19a55e479d24412d5098adce87bbd73ae6176165c1d","item_id":"c1812aa016:9","text":"PxrBlend"}
{"id":"50fb68245d43517e4ab4c41deced111e806f4f0e5dbd69c8694975cf7425c26b","item_id":"c1812aa016:2","text":" 类似的功能，但可以组合最多 8 个 layer，而不是只使用 top 和 bottom layer。它还包含一个额外的 background（背景）或 base（基底）layer。"}
{"id":"5032ab2ec3726cb8e813f257ef801cd00f0f24d7b91dbaf20bf86a0cb84857ec","item_id":"c1812aa016:4","text":"每个 layer 暴露以下参数，其中 [x] 是 0 到 7 之间的数字。Layers 按如下顺序排列：layer 7 位于底部，layer 0 是最顶层 layer。"}
{"id":"86acf109d1e552d9e6fd4470b55e777ed28084b57e5aba90d799351611dba978","item_id":"c1812aa016:5","text":"Enable [x]"}
{"id":"1ccc989c0feef3a0a4b0e4e1f1b8801094738061f356252c81daf83ab47f6558","item_id":"c1812aa016:6","text":"这会启用 layer [x] 以供使用。"}
{"id":"0fc38249859675301701115478c831df333a7b184a9690f90dfb42ee8e328518","item_id":"c1812aa016:7","text":"Operation [x]"}
{"id":"de787d343b26c1dfca70fe5f37f7f7a33d0b7de2b099fb94172d35ffb899a280","item_id":"c1812aa016:8","text":"用于将当前 layer 与前一个 layer 混合的 blend mode。此参数的行为与"}
{"id":"edc00d4db80ddc3e91783b63ae5fbcdfd204de983c650e9587785a40271c8f3c","item_id":"c1812aa016:10","text":" 的"}
{"id":"47b22d08e319f9a0807b60794c2a859df4f5f1e18fc44550ef51ba44b55c6e4a","item_id":"c1812aa016:11","text":"operation 相同。"}
{"id":"9bd998db95a7d5dbb9a38833f5f873145329d027e807e17e44beee2fc6cb8f8b","item_id":"c1812aa016:12","text":"Color [x]"}
{"id":"ef372b1d8e22e0f87b01ef451adfdd76d1447d23df9b7c83aa5c905c3afdc534","item_id":"c1812aa016:13","text":"图像 layer [x] 的 RGB 输入。"}
{"id":"34c207676c8dce2ae4c7e8882a396a46dbee56f82c45c2a46de8178a7bacf56b","item_id":"c1812aa016:14","text":"Alpha [x]"}
{"id":"75b9c759cb9c3566a8d72c29adda5f049bfb128393a68832bf045244bff31b75","item_id":"c1812aa016:15","text":"图像 layer [x] 的 alpha channel。当 alpha < 1 时，此图像 layer 下方会使用黑色背景。"}
{"id":"b48bc969e914f8c99f057fe30244969190bab97e709a7be85e820e792005243f","item_id":"c1812aa016:16","text":"Background Color"}
{"id":"fd347f3d3c3c2f2ebed59ed4aa5918b94e06204b3d459ea723719816a8af306e","item_id":"c1812aa016:17","text":"bottom 或 base 图像的 RGB 输入。"}
{"id":"f4c06e661055997e206abe727ec11dca6727c70e64476ecc0d9b606f5c0fd1ed","item_id":"c1812aa016:18","text":"Background Alpha"}
{"id":"108be93d1a00086ed2b27a04a0627f398b938400f71eaaf6692f57e02621a4f8","item_id":"c1812aa016:19","text":"bottom 或 base 图像的 alpha channel 或 mask。"}
{"id":"b7a76c00bd2a1e4e0c370838996637327e8c205e890f72b539a81a7abc5874e3","item_id":"c1812aa016:21","text":"所有 layer 的结果颜色都会被钳制到 1.0"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "c1812aa016:3", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "79dc22e6ed3847c8ad58d2465a5b2897aa5d9033fdf3f4b131d51621133273f7", "item_id": "c1812aa016:20", "text": "Clamp Output"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "c1812aa016:22", "text": "Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "c1812aa016:23", "text": "resultRGB"}
{"id": "6796d2c52b4882b98311c8be5b2889976246b071d35733a80a01da19e5bcba42", "item_id": "c1812aa016:24", "text": "钳制后的颜色结果。"}
{"id": "c9223602a8320733dcf0de118c9880f9df06acdfdb068bb26ba166fc96c52d6c", "item_id": "c1812aa016:25", "text": "resultR"}
{"id": "c1ce276296aa97e85eded6362e0ad2b80973bc92228513facedd911006df8937", "item_id": "c1812aa016:26", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 R 通道。"}
{"id": "2e12f103dc4a4b216b21cc6f017371b08507fc67f2a1ad9f133aa333afe0fc11", "item_id": "c1812aa016:27", "text": "resultG"}
{"id": "009cc7a7eb8d7664fe8e8a024e817626113dd5198fc3a164f5ec297f2fa68da3", "item_id": "c1812aa016:28", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 G 通道。"}
{"id": "c3719f180d82ecafb70ce347c3499e7668a3d9262533cadae303c770922865ff", "item_id": "c1812aa016:29", "text": "resultB"}
{"id": "d1e2217f59ea1bd29de7ec3ac2c05c763eca2c3bf612f3e04ff7cfd536f9f8e0", "item_id": "c1812aa016:30", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 B 通道。"}
